-- Lebanon to Auction Offshore Natural-Gas Contracts in 2012, Minister Says
-- B y   N a y l a   R a z z o u k
-- 2010-09-30T08:59:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/lebanon-to-auction-offshore-natural-gas-contracts-in-2012-minister-says.html
Lebanon plans to auction contracts
for offshore natural gas exploration in 2012, Energy Minister
Gebran Bassil said in an interview in Beirut today.  “Until then, we will be preparing all necessary documents
for the process,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
